Where round the year his devotee are visiting and on every Poonam they visit in mass.

text.text: This temple is an ancient temple built around 14th century CE in Paramara style. The temple is standing on a platform where benches has been placed so that visitors can sit. The temple is a quite place, surrounded by lush green trees and crops. The temple has beautiful carved mouldings and the superstructure is built in typical Bhumija shikhar. A well and a handpump is also there in the complex. If someone is interested in seeing old, beautiful intricate craftsmanship this temple should be in their bucket list.

text.text:
Shree charbhujanath ji temple
Shree Charbhujanath ji is present in the middle along with the idol of Shri Radha Krishna ji and the statue of Shree Lakshmi Mata.
He got very beautiful and beautiful darshan.
Every year, Chappan Bhog and Bhandara is also organized here. From the side of Shree Bade Hanuman he reached the mountain where this temple resides.

originalText.text:
Shree charbhujanath ji mandir
Madhya me Shree charbhujanath ji viraman he   Un ke sath shree radha krishna ji ki atyant manihari pratima avm shree laxmi mata ki pratima.
Atyant sundar avm manohari darshan prapt hote he.
Prativarsh yaha chhappan bhog avm bhandare ka ayojan bhi kiya jata he.  Shree bade hanuman ji ke pas se upar ko rasta he jaha yah mandir virajman he
